HEADWORD: Half-caste
<hw>Half"-caste`</hw> <pr>(-k⟦adot⟧st)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One born
of a European parent on the one side, and of a Hindu or Muslim on the
other. Also adjective; <as>as, <ex>half-caste</ex>
parents</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

